title: Grateful Dead Live at Madison Square Garden on 1991-09-17
lineage: 16 bit 48kHz DAT Master > TASCAM DA-20 (SPDIF out) ->  LynxTWO-B Audio Reference Interface (SPDIF in) ->  Wavelab 6.0 by Todd Evans (todd@bluedakota.com) October 30, 2008   Editing and Mastering: Jamie Waddell (shnflac@gmail.com) on the GEMS Edit Station.  Weiss Saracon for 16 BIT 44.1kHz SRC and POWR-3 Dither  Encoding by Dazed64. Tracked in CDwave, FLAC with Flac Frontend level 8 Tag & Rename for FLAC Meta-Tagging
description:
Set 1

Iko Iko 
Greatest Story Ever Told 
Althea 
Little Red Rooster 
Loser 
It's All Over Now 
Brown Eyed Women 
Picasso Moon 

Set 2

Box Of Rain 
Cold Rain And Snow 
Samson And Delilah 
Eyes Of The World ->
Drums ->
Space ->
The Last Time ->
Black Peter ->
Throwing Stones ->
Not Fade Away 

Encore
U.S. Blues
